itemDescription: Born: 26 May 1885 in Kinghorn, Fife, Scotland; Died: 16 December 1946 in Radcliffe Infirmary, Oxford

wikipedia_page.main: Prof William Barron Coutts FRSE (26 May 1885 – 16 December 1946) was a Scottish physicist specialising in military science. He was generally referred to as Willie Coutts.
